# Card template contract

- Location: this directory (`data/templates/`).
- Filenames: one per card using rank+suit, e.g., `As.png`, `Kd.png`, `2c.png`.
- Template type: **corner-only** rank+suit crops (recommended for robustness).
- Pixel size: fixed 40x40 px per template (adjust here if your UI differs).
- Color: grayscale (single channel); RGB/BGR images will be converted but keep sizes consistent.
- Expectation: all 52 templates present; missing files mean card detection stays disabled.

Notes:
- If templates are absent, the pipeline will log “0 templates loaded, card detection disabled”.
- Keep capture viewport and crop regions fixed so templates match future screenshots.
